summary: USAMA called to make a complaint about a pack that is abhi apke pas hai (expiring on 23/05). The complainant's name is Hrishikesh Meshram, the address is Vijaynagar, Hingna, Nagpur, and the manufacturing date is 23/05. The expiration date is 13/02/24. The cash number is on the manufacturing gate and is still open. The packet replacement is a goodwill gesture. The complaint register will inform the complainant that they have to pay the complaint number. The EC number will be provided to the complainant before the executive visits the address. The complainant will be called to provide more information and informed that the executive will visit their address.  The call was long and confusing at times due to language difficulties.  Ultimately, the caller is making an effort to provide good customer service and ensure that the complainant is informed of the status of their complaint.  The call ends with the caller thanking the complainant and telling them to have a great day.  The complainant will be called again to provide an EC number.  The executive will visit the complainant's address.  The complaint will be resolved.  The customer service being provided is good.
speaker_a_summary: A customer called a customer service center and is looking for help with a complaint about a product they purchased. They are speaking in Hindi and provides the name Hrishikesh Meshram, and address in Nagpur as a contact. They are looking to report an issue with expiration dates on a product they purchased, specifically mentioning a mother who consumed it and had a bad reaction. The customer is looking for help with a video they have and is put on hold. The customer gets frustrated and wants to speak to a higher authority.
speaker_b_summary: Hrishikesh Mishra is making a complaint about a packet that they received, they want to know about its expiration date, and they also would like to know when its manufacturing date was. They also want to know the manufacturing location, and the batch number. They will be given a call as a goodwill gesture to replace the packet. They will also be given a call regarding the complaint and will be informed of the executive that will visit them to collect the packet as a goodwill gesture.
